[This particular pathogen causes a variety of clinical signs from respiratory, to arthritis, and mastitis, and can be difficult to diagnose. It can be an aggressive pathogen, therefore it is not unexpected that MPI has found, and expects to find more cases of this disease. Hopefully this agent will not spread any farther and in a best case scenario, this will be the last infected premises. - Mod.TG

